  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK836">
<l>poypaṭu moṉṟō puṉaipūṇuṅ kaiyaṟiyāp</l>
<l>pētai viṉaimēṟ koḷiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If the fool, who knows not how to act undertakes a work, he will (certainly) fail. (But) is it all ? He will even adorn himself with fetters.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
